Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and set those objects properties in a much more simplified succinct syntax
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,(It) took us 12 lines of code, 13 lines of code C#
