Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So okay that's it, that's the point of this lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Two fold, one that XAML is just a specific flavor of XML
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It follows all the rules of XML
