Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they can begin to work together, konwing that they are pretty much on the same page
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now in this case, the contract is XAML and it was defined by Microsoft
